Sɑɑ yèn di i dĩɑnu ɡɛ̃ɛbu toruɑ, i ko i ɑlusumɑ ɡɑriwɑ yu kɑ ko nɔɔbɑ yiru.
Tire te, tɑ ko n wɑ̃ɑwɑ win bɔkuɔ kpɑ u n dɑ tu ɡɑri tɔ̃ɔ bɑɑtere win wɑ̃ɑrun tɔ̃ru kpuro sɔɔ kpɑ u kɑ ɡiɑ nɡe mɛ u koo Gusunɔ win Yinni nɑsiɑ, u win woodɑbɑ kɑ win yiirebu mɛm nɔɔwɑ.
Nɡe mɛyɑ bɑ ǹ koo mɑɑ be bɑ kun toren yɛm yɑri tem mɛ sɔɔ mɛ Gusunɔ bɛsɛn Yinni u bɛɛ wɛ̃ i n mɔ, kpɑ yɛ̃ron yɛm mu kun wɑ̃ɑ bɛɛn winɔ.
Dɑ̃ɑ te i yɛ̃ tɑ ǹ sɑ̃ɑ diirɑru, terɑ i ko i kpĩ i burɑ i kɑ sɛri ko yi i ko i kɑ ɡbɑ̃rɑru yɔ sere i kɑ wuu ɡe kɑmiɑ.
Ì n dii kpɑɑru bɑnɑ i kpɑ, i ten tɛɛrɑ wɔllɔ ɡɑni dumi dokeo i kɑ sikerenɑ kpɑ bɑɑ ɡoo ù n wɔrumɑ min di u ɡu, i kun tɑɑrɛ mɔ.
Ì n yɑrɑ i kɑ yibɛrɛbɑ tɑbu wɔri, sɑɑ ye sɔɔrɑ i ko i tii lɑɑkɑri ko kɑ ɡɑ̃ɑ disiɡinu kpuro.
Bɑ ǹ tɔnu ɡoomɔ win biin torɑrun sɔ̃, mɛyɑ bɑ ǹ mɑɑ bii ɡoomɔ win mɔwɔbun torɑrun sɔ̃. Bɑ ǹ ɡoo ɡoomɔ ɡoon torɑrun sɔ̃.
Adɑmɑ Eɡibitiɡibu bɑ bu dɑm dɔre, bɑ bu nɔni sɔ̃ɔwɑ, mɑ bɑ bu kuɑ yobu.
Kpɑ Lefibɑ bu nɛɛ, bɔ̃rurowɑ wi u win winsim tem nɔɔ burɑ yeru sɑre. Kpɑ tɔmbu kpuro bu nɛɛ, ɑmi!
U koo de bɛɛn wɑsi yi ɡberɑ ǹ kun mɛ yi swĩɑ ǹ kun mɛ yi mɔsi ǹ kun mɛ yi wooru bɑrɑ. U koo mɑɑ yinɑ ɡurɑ yu nɛ kpɑ bɛɛn ɡbeɑn dĩɑnu nu ɡberɑ ǹ kun mɛ nu kɔ̃si. Wɑhɑlɑ ye kpurowɑ i ko wɑ sere u kɑ bɛɛ kpeerɑsiɑ mɑm mɑm.
Sɑnɑm mɛ bɛɛn yibɛrɛ be, bɑ bɛɛ tɑrusi, ɡɔ̃ɔrɑ koo ko sere i bɛɛn bibu tem be Yinni Gusunɔ u bɛɛ wɛ̃.
Yen sɔ̃, bɛɛn suunu sɔɔ, ɡoo ǹ kun mɛ yɛnu ɡɑɡu ǹ kun mɛ bwese kɛrɑ ɡɑɑ yu ku rɑɑ Gusunɔ bɛsɛn Yinni biru kisi kpɑ yu dɑ yu bwese tuku nin bũnu sɑ̃. Bɛɛn suunu sɔɔ, ɡoo u ku rɑɑ ɡɔsirɑ u ko nɡe dɑ̃ɑ ye yɑ dɛ̃ɛ mɔ.
Kpɑ i Gusunɔ bɛsɛn Yinni kĩɑ i n kɑ nùn mɑninɛ kpɑ i n nùn mɛm nɔɔwɑmmɛ. Domi yerɑ yɑ koo de i n wɑ̃ɑ kpɑ yu bɛɛn wɑ̃ɑru dɛnyɑsiɑ i kɑ wɑ i n wɑ̃ɑ tem mɛ sɔɔ, mɛ u bɛsɛn sikɑdobɑ Aburɑhɑmu kɑ Isɑki kɑ Yɑkɔbu nɔɔ mwɛɛru kuɑ.
Mɑ Mɔwisi u womu ɡenin ɡɑri kpuro ɡeruɑ, mɑ Isirelibɑ kpuro bɑ yi nuɑ. Ge wee.
U ben lɑɑkɑri mɔ nɡe win tiin nɔni.
Bɑ win mɔru kɑ win nisinu seeyɑ
Ǹ kun mɛ tɔmbu yiru bu tɔmbu nɔrɔbun subɑ wɔkuru (10.000) yɑrinɑsiɑ?
Nɛnɑ nɑ rɑ mɛɛrɑ ko
mɑ u win tɔmbu yɑm bururɑsiɑ sɑɑ Pɑrɑnin ɡuurun di.
kpɑ bu turɑre dɔ̃ɔ doke wunɛn yɑ̃ku yerɔ.
Kpɑ ɑ de Isɑkɑrin bwese kɛrɑ yɑ n wɑ̃ɑ bɔri yɛndu sɔɔ yen kunɔ.
Yerɑ Mɔwisi u kpɑm ɡeruɑ u nɛɛ,
U nɛɛ, wee, nɛn sɔm kowo Mɔwisi u ɡu. Ǹ n mɛn nɑ, ɑ seewo ɑ Yuudɛni ye tɔburɑ, wunɛ kɑ Isirelibɑ kpuro i dɑ tem mɛ nɑ bu wɛ̃ɛmɔ sɔɔ.
Durɔ be, bɑ nùn sɔ̃ɔwɑ bɑ nɛɛ, yèn nɔɔ mwɛɛru sɑ kuɑ kɑ bɔ̃ri mi, sɑ ko ye ko. Adɑmɑ wee ye wunɛn tii kɑɑ ko.
kpɑ su bu sɔ̃ mɑ Yuudɛnin dɑɑrun nim mu kokubu yɔ̃rɑ Yinni Gusunɔn kpɑkororun wuswɑɑɔ sɑnɑm mɛ bɑ kɑ tu tɔburɔ. Kpee nini nu ko n sɑ̃ɑ yen seedɑ bɛsɛ Isirelibɑn sɔ̃ sere kɑ bɑɑdommɑɔ.
Durɔ wi, u wisɑ u nɛɛ, ɑɑwo, nɑ ǹ yen ɡoo. Nɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ Yinni Gusunɔn tɑbu kowobun wiruɡii. Yen sɔ̃nɑ nɑ nɑ wunɛn mi tɛ̃.
Ù n kpɛɛkpɛɛku surɑmɔ,
Mɑ bɑ kpenu ɡurɑ bɑ nin tɑkɑnu kuɑ ben wɔllɔ te tɑ wɑ̃ɑ mi sere kɑ ɡisɔ. Ye kpuron sɔ̃nɑ bɑ yɑm mi sokumɔ Akɔɔn wɔwɑ sere kɑ ɡisɔn ɡisɔ. Yĩsi ten tubusiɑnɑ, nɔni swɑ̃ɑrun wɔwɑ.
U yɑ̃ku yee te bɑnɑwɑ nɡe mɛ Mɔwisi, Yinni Gusunɔn sɔm kowo u Isirelibɑ sɔ̃ɔwɑ ye u yoruɑ woodɑbɑn tireru sɔɔ. U nɛɛ, bu Yinni Gusunɔ yɑ̃ku yeru kuo kɑ kpee ni bɑ ǹ dɑ̃ke. Ye bɑ tu bɑnɑ bɑ kpɑ mɑ bɑ yɑ̃ku dɔ̃ɔ mwɑɑrɑruɡinu kɑ siɑrɑbun yɑ̃kunu kuɑ mi.
Adoni Sedɛki, Yerusɑlɛmun sunɔ u nuɑ mɑ Yosue u Ayi kɑmiɑ u ye kpeerɑsiɑ u yen sunɔ ɡo, nɡe mɛ u rɑɑ Yeriko kɑ yen sunɔ kuɑ. U mɑɑ nuɑ mɑ Gɑbɑoniɡibu bɑ kɑ Isirelibɑ ɑrukɑwɑni bɔkuɑ, bɑ wɑ̃ɑ ben suunu sɔɔ.
Yen biru sɑɑ Mɑkedɑn di, Yosue kɑ win tɔn be, bɑ dɑ bɑ Libinɑ wɔri.
Sinɑm be bɑ kɑmiɑ mi, ben wusu wɑ̃ɑwɑ sɑɑ ɡuu tèn mi ɡɑ̃ɑnu ku rɑ kpin berɑ ɡiɑn di Seirin bɔkuɔ, sɔ̃ɔ yɛ̃sɑn nɔm dwɑru ɡiɑ n kɑ ɡirɑri Bɑɑli Gɑdiɔ ye yɑ wɑ̃ɑ Libɑnin wɔwɑɔ ɡuu te bɑ mɔ̀ Hɛɛmɔɔn ɡɑ̃ɑrɔ sɔ̃ɔ yɛ̃sɑn nɔm ɡeu ɡiɑ.
Mɛyɑ Filisitibɑn tem kɑ Gesuribɑn tem
Adɑmɑ u ǹ Lefin bwese kɛrɑ tem ɡɑm wɛ̃. U bu sɔ̃ɔwɑ bu ko Gusunɔ ben Yinnin yɑ̃ku kowobu. Yeyɑ yɑ ko n sɑ̃ɑ ben tubi, nɡe mɛ Yinni Gusunɔ u ɡeruɑ.
Heboronin diyɑ u seewɑ u dɑ u Debiriɡibu wɔri. Wuu ɡerɑ bɑ rɑ rɑɑ soku Sefɛɛn wuu.
Kɑ mɑɑ Ekoroni, ye kɑ yen wuu mɑrosu kɑ yen bɑru kpɑɑnu.
Gɑlɑdi, Mɑkirin bii, Mɑnɑsen debubu u Efɛɛ mɑrɑ. Efɛɛ wi, u Selofɑdi mɑrɑ. Selofɑdi wi, u ǹ bii tɔn durɔ mɑrɑ, sere tɔn kurɔbu tɔnɑ. Bii ben yĩsɑ wee. Mɑlɑ kɑ Nɔɑ kɑ Hoɡulɑ kɑ Milikɑ kɑ Tirisɑ.
Sɔ̃ɔ yɛ̃sɑn nɔm dwɑru ɡiɑ mɑɑ, tɑ dɑwɑ sɔ̃ɔ duu yeru ɡiɑ sɑɑ Yɑrimun wuun di sere Nɛfitoɑn bwiiyɔ.
Berɑ yeni kpurowɑ yɑ kuɑ Sɑbulonin bwese kɛrɑɡiɑ.
Sɑnɑm mɛ Dɑnubɑ bɑ wɑ yibɛrɛbɑ bɑ kpɑm ben tem mwɛɛrimɔ, yerɑ be, bɑ mɑɑ dɑ bɑ Lesɛmu wɔri bɑ yen tɔmbu kpuro ɡo. Mɑ bɑ yɑnde sinɑ mi, yɑ kuɑ ben wuu. Yerɑ bɑ ye ben sikɑdon yĩsiru kɑ̃ te bɑ mɔ̀ Dɑnu.
Wuu si kpuro, si bɑ yɑ̃ku kowo Aronin bweseru wɛ̃ su sɑ̃ɑwɑ wɔkurɑ itɑ, ɡen bɑɑɡere kɑ ɡen kpɑrɑ yenu.
Mɑ Rubɛnibɑ kɑ Gɑdibɑ kɑ Mɑnɑse be, bɑ ɡɔsirɑ bɑ dɑ ben temɔ bɑ Isirelibɑn bwese kɛri yi yi tie deri, Kɑnɑnin tem mi. Bɑ dɑ bɑ sinɑ Gɑlɑdin temɔ nɡe mɛ Yinni Gusunɔ u ɡeruɑ sɑɑ win sɔm kowo Mɔwisin nɔɔn di.
Yen sɔ̃, i tɛmɑnɔ, i hɑniɑ koowo kpɑ i wɑ i woodɑ ye mɛm nɔɔwɑ ye Mɔwisi u yoruɑ tireru sɔɔ kpɑ i ku yen ɡɑɑ ɡɛɛrɑri bɑɑ fiiko.
Yosue u bu sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, bɛɛ, i bɛɛn tii seedɑ diiyɑ mɑ Yinni Gusunɔwɑ i ɡɔsɑ i sɑ̃.
Yen biru Yudɑbɑ kɑ ben mɑɑbu Simɛɔbɑ bɑ Kɑnɑni be bɑ wɑ̃ɑ Sefɑtiɔ wɔri bɑ kpeerɑsiɑ mɑm mɑm. Wuu ɡerɑ bɑ yĩsiru kɑ̃ Hɔɔmɑ. Yen tubusiɑnɑ bɑnsu.
12-13 Bɑ Gusunɔ ben bɑɑbɑbɑn yinni deri wi u bu yɑrɑmɑ Eɡibitin di. Mɑ bɑ be bɑ bu sikerenɛn bũu ni bɑ mɔ̀ Bɑɑlibɑ kɑ Asitɑɑtebɑ sɑ̃ɑmɔ bɑ nu wiru kpĩiyɑmmɛ. Yerɑ n derɑ Yinni Gusunɔn mɔru seewɑ.
Mɑ sinɑ boko u nɛɛ, win sinɑ bwɑ̃ɑbu bu ɡinɑ yɑrio be kpuro.
Ye bɑ Siserɑ kɑ win tɑbu kowobu kɑ win tɑbu kɛkɛbɑ wɔri, Yinni Gusunɔ u derɑ Siserɑn tɔn be, bɑ burisinɑ Bɑrɑkin wuswɑɑɔ. Mɑ Siserɑ u sɑrɑ win kɛkɛn di u dukɑ suɑ kɑ nɑɑsu.
Wiruɡii ɡoo sɑri wi u dɑm mɔ Isirelibɑ sɔɔ,
Isɑkɑribɑn wiruɡibu bɑ kɑ Deborɑ yɔ̃rɑ.
Kɑɑ domɑru wɑ, Yɑɛli, Hebɛɛ Kenin kurɔ.
U bɛɛ wɔrɑ ben nɔmɑn di kɑ sere mɑɑ be bɑ bɛɛ dɑm dɔremɔ kpuron nɔmɑn di. Mɑ u be kpuro ɡirɑ bɛɛn wuswɑɑn di. U ben tem mwɑ u bɛɛ wɛ̃.
Wee, kon yɑ̃ɑ sɑn sini yi temɔ ɑlikɑmɑ soo yerɔ. Ǹ n kuɑ bururu, dirum mù n wɑ̃ɑ yɑ̃ɑ sɑn si tɔnɑ sɔɔ, kpɑ ɑlikɑmɑ soo yee te kpuro tɑ n ɡbere, sɑnɑm mɛ sɔɔrɑ kon ɡiɑ mɑ ɡeemɑ, kɑɑ Isirelibɑ fɑɑbɑ kowɑ sɑɑ nɛn min di nɡe mɛ ɑ ɡeruɑ.
Yerɑ Efɑrɑimubɑ kpuro bɑ mɛnnɑ bɑ dɑ bɑ swɑɑ burɑ Yuudɛnin tɔbusun di sere n kɑ ɡirɑri Bɛti Bɑrɑɔ.
N deemɑ Mɑdiɑnibɑ bɑ swɑɑ tonku wurɑɡinu mɔ, domi bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ Isimɛɛlin bweseru.
Tɛ̃ ye i Gedeoni kɑ win yɛnuɡibu kuɑ mi, ì n ye kuɑn nɑ kɑ nuku tiɑ murɑfitiru sɑri, Gusunɔ u de bɛɛ kɑ Abimɛlɛki i n wɑ̃ɑsinɛ kɑ nuku dobu.
Mɑ ben bɑɑwure u dɑ̃ɑ kɑ̃ɑsɑ burɑ u seru sɔndi bɑ kɑ nùn swĩi. Mɑ be kpuro bɑ ben dɑ̃ɑ ye sure wɔru ɡen kɔnnɔwɔ. Yen biru bɑ ye dɔ̃ɔ doke. Mɑ Sikɛmuɡii be bɑ wɑ̃ɑ wɔru ɡe sɔɔ kpuro bɑ dɔ̃ɔ mwɑɑrɑ. Bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ tɔmbu nɔrɔbu (1.000), kurɔbu kɑ durɔbu.
Yen biru Amɔnibɑ bɑ Isirelibɑ wɔri.
Sɑnɑm mɛ u bii wi wɑ, yerɑ u win tiin yɑberu nɛnuɑ u kɑrɑnɑ nuku sɑnkirɑnun sɔ̃, u nɔɔɡiru suɑ u nɛɛ, nɛn bii, nuku sɑnkirɑ bɑkɑnu sɔɔrɑ ɑ mɑn doke mi. Domi nɑ Yinni Gusunɔ nɔɔ mwɛɛru kuɑ. Tɑǹ mɑɑ kɔbiɑrɔ.
Mɑ Gusunɔ u Mɑnɔɑn kɑnɑru mwɑ, u derɑ win ɡɔrɑdo wi, u wurɑ kurɔ win mi, mi u sɔ̃ ɡberɔ. Adɑmɑ win durɔ sɑri mi.
Mɑ Sɑnsom u bu sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, kon bɛɛ sukuru ɡɑru kuɑ. Sere n kɑ ko kurɔ kpɑɑ ten sɔ̃ɔ nɔɔbɑ yiru, kpɑ i mɑn tu tubusiɑ. Ì n tu tubɑ, kon bɛɛn bɑɑwure yɑberu kɛ̃ kɑ tɔ̃ɔ bɑkɑ yɑ̃nu.
Sɑnsom u bu wisɑ u nɛɛ, nɡe mɛ ben tii bɑ mɑn kuɑ, nɡe mɛyɑ nɑ mɑɑ bu kuɑ.
Ye Sɑnsom u dweeyɑ, mɑ Dɑlilɑ u win wirun tɑri yi mɛnnɑ kɑ wɛ̃ɛ siiri u wesɑ. Mɑ u kɑ yi dɑ̃ru kpɑresi temɔ. Yerɑ u nùn yɑmiɑ u nɛɛ, Sɑnsom, Filisitibɑ wee, bɑ nun wɔrimɑ.
N deemɑ Mikɑ u rɑɑ sɑ̃ɑ yeru mɔ win yɛnuɔ. Mɑ u derɑ bɑ nùn bwɑ̃ɑroku ɡɑnu kuɑ. Mɑ u win tiin bii turo ɡɔsɑ u kuɑ nin yɑ̃ku kowo.
Mɑ Dɑnu be, bɑ ɡurenɑ bɑ doonɑ, bɑ ben bibu ɡbiisie kɑ yɑɑ sɑbenu kɑ sere ben sɔmunu.
Mɑ u kɑ tɔn be dɑ win yɛnuɔ u ben kɛtɛkunu dĩɑnu wɛ̃. Ben tii bɑ ben nɑɑsu kpɑkiɑ, mɑ u bu dĩɑnu wɛ̃ bɑ dimɔ bɑ nɔrumɔ
Mɑ Isireli be, bɑ dɑ Betɛliɔ bu kɑ Gusunɔ bikiɑ u bu sɔ̃ɔsi bwese kɛrɑ ye yɑ koo ɡbi yu Bɛnyɑmɛɛbɑ wɔri. Mɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u Yudɑbɑ ɡɔsɑ.
Isirelibɑ bɑ ɡɔsirɑmɑ bɑ nɑ Bɛnyɑmɛɛ be bɑ tien wusu sɔɔ. Bɑ bu ɡo ɡo sere kɑ ben yɑɑ sɑbenɔ. Hunde koni ye yɑ wɑ̃ɑ mi kpuro ɡesi, bɑ ɡowɑ. Mɑ bɑ ben wuu si kpuro dɔ̃ɔ mɛni.
6-7 Yenibɑn biru, Nɑomi u nuɑ Gusunɔ u win tɔmbu durom kuɑ u bu dĩɑnu wɛ̃. Yerɑ u seewɑ sɔ̃ɔ teeru kɑ win biɡii kurɔbu Mɔɑbun di, bɑ wiɔ Yudɑn temɔ.
Sɑnɑm mɛ bɑ dimɔ, Boɑsi u nùn sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, ɑ susimɑ ɑ pɛ̃ɛ suɑ ɑ sɔ̃re kpee sɔɔ kpɑ ɑ di.
Yen biru, u dwɑɑ mɛro sɑɑriɑ ye Boɑsi u nùn kuɑ.
Adɑmɑ Hɑnɑɡiɑ u rɑ de yɑ n kpɑ̃ɑru bo. Domi u nùn kĩ bɑɑ mɛ Yinni Gusunɔ u nùn kuɑ wĩro.
U sɑ̃ɑwɑ nɡe kpee bɑɑ mi nɑ rɑ kuke.
Adɑmɑ u koo de tɔn kɔ̃sobu
Yen sɔ̃, u nɛɛ, wiyɑ u rɑɑ ɡeruɑ mɑ wunɛn yɛnu kɑ wunɛn bɑɑbɑn yɛnuɡibu bɑ koo ko win yɑ̃ku kowobu sere kɑ bɑɑdommɑɔ. Adɑmɑ tɛ̃ u ɡeruɑ u nɛɛ, yɑ ǹ mɑɑ koorɔ mɛ, domi be bɑ nùn bɛɛrɛ wɛ̃ɛmɔ, beyɑ u koo bɛɛrɛ wɛ̃. Be bɑ kun nùn ɡɑrɑ, beyɑ u ǹ ɡɑrisimɔ.
Sɑmuɛli u kpunɑ sere n kɑ kuɑ sisiru. Mɑ u sɑ̃ɑ yerun ɡɑmbobɑ kɛniɑ. Adɑmɑ u ǹ kɑ̃kɑ u Eli kɑ̃si ten ɡɑri yi sɔ̃.
Filisitibɑ bɑ Gusunɔn woodɑn kpɑkoro te suɑ sɑɑ Ebɛni Esɛɛn di bɑ kɑ dɑ Asidɔduɔ,
Bwisinun weenɑsii ni Filisitibɑ bɑ kuɑ kɑ wurɑ bɑ Yinni Gusunɔ wɛ̃ ben durum sɔ̃, bɑ nu kuɑwɑ wuu sinin sɔ̃, Asidɔdu kɑ Gɑsɑ kɑ Asikɑloni kɑ Gɑti kɑ mɑɑ Ekoroni.
Mɑ Sɑmuɛli u Yinni Gusunɔn ɡɑri yi kpuro tɔn be tusiɑ.
Sɑmuɛli u Sɔɔlu wisɑ u nɛɛ, nɛnɑ yɑm wɑo wi. A nɑ su dɑ ɡunɡuru mi. Sɑnnɑ sɑ ko di ɡisɔ. Ǹ n kuɑ bururu, ye ɑ bwisikumɔ wunɛn ɡɔ̃ruɔ ɑ bikiɑ, kon nun ye kpuro wisi, kpɑ n de ɑ doonɑ.
Adɑmɑ wee, i nùn yinɑ ɡisɔ, wi u bɛɛ fɑɑbɑ kuɑ bɛɛn wɑhɑlɑ kɑ bɛɛn nɔni swɑ̃ɑrun di. Mɑ i nɛɛ, u bɛɛ sunɔ kuo, u bɛɛ kpɑrɑ. Ǹ n mɛn nɑ, i yɑrimɑ bweseru kɑ bweseru, kpɑ i tii tusiɑ yɛnu kɑ yɛnu win wuswɑɑɔ.
Bɑ nɛɛ, ɑ ǹ sun tɑki diire, ɑ ǹ mɑɑ sun dɑm dɔrere. Mɛyɑ ɑ ǹ mɑɑ bɛsɛn ɡoon kɛ̃ru mwɑɑre ɑ kɑ nùn ɡem wɛ̃.
Bɑ tɛ mi, bɑ kuɑwɑ sɔ̃ɔ nɔɔbɑ yiru nɡe mɛ Sɑmuɛli u Sɔɔlu burɑ, ɑdɑmɑ Sɑmuɛli u ǹ nɛ. Yerɑ tɔmbɑ yɑrinɑm toruɑ.
Ben tɑbun tore ye sɔɔ, be yiru ye, bɑ tɔmbu ɡowɑ nɡe tɔnu yɛndun sɑkɑ bɑtumɑ piibu sɔɔ.
Yerɑ Sɔɔlu u nɛɛ, i mɛnnɑmɑ bɛɛ be i sɑ̃ɑ wiruɡibu kpɑ su ɡiɑ mi torɑrɑ wɑ̃ɑ ɡisɔ.
Ye Sɑmuɛli u ɡɑri yi nuɑ, yerɑ u mɔru kuɑ ɡem ɡem, mɑ u Yinni Gusunɔ nɔɔɡiru sue wɔ̃ku ɡiriru.
Mɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u nɛɛ, ɑ nɑɑ ɡbiibɑ suo kpɑ ɑ nɛɛ, ɑ nɑwɑ ɑ kɑ mɑn yɑ̃kuru kuɑ.
U mɑɑ sii ɡɑndun kɔrɔm doke, mɑ u sii ɡɑndun yɑɑsɑ bɛki.
Yinni Gusunɔ wi u mɑn wɔrɑ sɑɑ ɡbee sunɔ kɑ yɑɑ kɔ̃sɑ yen min di u koo mɑɑ mɑn wɔrɑ Filisiti win nɔmɑn di.
Sɑɑ yè sɔɔ tɑbu kowobɑ wee tɑbu ɡberun di, mi Dɑfidi u Filisiti wi ɡo, yerɑ tɔn kurɔbɑ yɑrimɑ Isirelibɑn wusu kpuron di bu kɑ Sɔɔlu sennɑ. Bɑ yɑɑmɔ bɑ bɑrɑnu kɑ mɔrɔkunu soomɔ, bɑ kuuki mɔ̀ kɑ nuku dobu.
Ye bɑ nɑ mi, Yonɑtɑm u win bɑɑ Dɑfidin ɡeɑ sɑɑriɑ u nɛɛ, wunɛ sunɔ ɑ ku wunɛn bɔ̃ɔ Dɑfidi torɑri. U ǹ nun kɔ̃sɑ ɡɑɑ kue. Ye u kuɑ kpuro, ɡɑ̃ɑ ɡeenɑ.
Yonɑtɑm u nɛɛ, ɑ ku yenin bweseru bwisiku. Nɑ̀ n ɡiɑ mɑ nɛn tundo u kĩ u nun kɔ̃sɑ kuɑ, kon nun sɔ̃.
Sɑɑ ye bii wi, u turɑ deedeeru mi sɛ̃u ɡe, ɡɑ dɑ, yerɑ Yonɑtɑm u kpɑm ɡbɑ̃rɑ u nɛɛ, ɡɑ wɑ̃ɑ wunɛn wuswɑɑɔ,
Mɑ Dɑfidi u seewɑ u dɑ u wɑ̃ɑ dɑ̃ɑ sɔ̃ɔ ɡe bɑ mɔ̀ Herɛtiɔ.
Yerɑ Sɔɔlu u win tɑbu kowobu kpuro mɛnnɑ bu dɑ bu kɑ Keilɑ wɔri, kpɑ bu Dɑfidi kɑ win tɔmbu tɑrusi.
Mɑ Sɔɔlu u seewɑ u yɑrɑ u doonɑ min di.
Yerɑ Nɑbɑlin sɔm kowo turo u nɑ u Abiɡɑli sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, wee, Dɑfidi u bɛsɛn yinni sɔmɔbu ɡɔriɑmɑ sɑɑ ɡbɑburun di bu nùn tɔbiri. Adɑmɑ u bu ɡirɑ kɑ dɑm,
Dɑfidi u rɑɑ mɑɑ Akinɔɑmu Yisirɛɛliɡii suɑ kurɔ. Mɑ be yiru ye, bɑ mɔre win mi.
Yenibɑn biru, Dɑfidi u tii sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, sɔ̃ɔ teeru Sɔɔlu u koo mɑn nɔmɑ turi u ɡo. Yen sɔ̃, n burɑm bo n dukɑ yɑkurɑ minin di n kpikiru dɑ Filisitibɑn temɔ kpɑ Sɔɔlu u ku mɑɑ mɑn kɑsu Isirelibɑn tem kpuro sɔɔ. Nɡe mɛyɑ kon kɑ wɑ n kisirɑ win nɔmɑn di.
Mɑ Sɔɔlu u ɡiɑ mɑ Sɑmuɛliwɑ. Mɑ u yiirɑ u wuswɑɑ tem ɡirɑri u nùn bɛɛrɛ wɛ̃.
Mɑ Dɑfidin nuki sɑnkirɑ too domi win tɔmbu bɑ ɡerunɑmɔ bɑ mɔ̀ bu nùn kpenu kɑsuku bu ɡo, yèn sɔ̃ bɑ ben kurɔbu kɑ bibu biɑ. Yerɑ n derɑ bɑ nuki sɑnkire. Adɑmɑ Dɑfidi u tii deri Yinni Gusunɔn nɔmuɔ. Mɑ u nùn dɑm kɑ̃.
kɑ Heboroniɡibu kɑ sere mɑɑ bèn mi wi Dɑfidi kɑ win tɔmbu bɑ rɑɑ dɑ dɑ.
14-16 Dɑfidi kpɑm nùn bikiɑ u nɛɛ, ɑmɔnɑ ɑ kɑ kɑ̃kɑ ɑ wi Yinni Gusunɔ ɡɔsɑ nɔmɑ doke ɑ ɡo. Yen sɔ̃, wunɛn yɛm mu yɔ̃rɑ wunɛn wiru wɔllɔ. Domi wunɛn tiin nɔɔwɑ ɡɑ seedɑ di mɑ ɑ wi Yinni Gusunɔ ɡɔsɑ ɡo.
Dɑmɡibɑ wɔrukɑ tɑbu ɡberɔ.
Yerɑ u dɔmɑ te Abinɛɛ nɑɑ ɡirɑ, u ǹ wure u nùn deri bɑɑ fiiko.
Mɑ Pɑtiɛli wi, u Mikɑli swĩi u sumɔ sere bɑ kɑ turɑ Bɑhurimuɔ. Mɑ Abinɛɛ u nùn sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, ɑ den ɡɔsiro. Yerɑ u ɡɔsirɑ u wurɑ win yɛnuɔ.
N deemɑ Yonɑtɑm, Sɔɔlun bii turo u bii tɔn durɔ mɔ wi bɑ mɔ̀ Mɛfibosɛti. Bii wi, u kuɑ yɛmɔ. Wɔ̃ɔ nɔɔbuwɑ u mɔ sɑnɑm mɛ Sɔɔlu kɑ Yonɑtɑm bɑ ɡu Yisirɛɛliɔ tɑbu sɔɔ. Ye kurɔ wi u bii wi nɔɔrimɔ u ɡɔɔ win lɑbɑɑri nuɑ, yerɑ u bii wi suɑ u kɑ doonɔ. Ye u dukɑ mɔ̀ kɑ sɛndɑru mɑ u wɔrumɑ u nùn surɑ. Min diyɑ bii wi, u kuɑ yɛmɔ.
Sɑnɑm mɛ ɑ nɑɑ dɑmu dɑmusu ɡɑsu nɔɔmɔ dɑ̃ɑ wɔllɔ, ɑ wɑsi suo, domi nɛ, Yinni Gusunɔwɑ nɑ nun ɡbiiye n kɑ ben sɑnsɑni wɔri.
Bɑɑmɑ mi sɑ dɑ nɛ kɑ Isirelibɑ ɡbɑburɔ, nɑ rɑ ben ɡɑbu ɡɔsiwɑ bɑ n kɑ be bɑ tie kpɑre. Adɑmɑ nɑ ǹ ben ɡoo tɑɑrɛ wɛ̃ɛre n nɛɛ, mbɑn sɔ̃nɑ u ǹ mɑn diru bɑniɛ kɑ dɑ̃ɑ ye bɑ mɔ̀ sɛduru.
yerɑ u win bii Yorɑmu ɡɔrɑ Dɑfidin mi, u kɑ nùn tɔbiri kpɑ u nùn siɑrɑ yèn sɔ̃ u Hɑdɑdesɛɛ tɑbu wɔri u kɑmiɑ. Domi Toi kɑ Hɑdɑdesɛɛ bɑ rɑɑ tɑbu wɔrinɛwɑ. Mɑ Yorɑmu u seewɑ u dendi yɑ̃ɑ ni bɑ kuɑ kɑ sii ɡeesu kɑ wurɑ kɑ sii ɡɑndu suɑ u kɑ Dɑfidi nɑɑwɑ.
Yerɑ ɡɑbɑ dɑ bɑ ye Dɑfidi sɔ̃ɔwɑ. Mɑ u tɔmbu seeyɑ bu nɑ bu bu sennɔ ko kpɑ bu bu sɔ̃ bu ɡinɑ sinɔ Yerikoɔ sere ben tobunu nù n kpiɑ. Domi bɑ wɑ̃ɑwɑ seku bɑkɑru sɔɔ.
Sisiru bururu yerɑ Dɑfidi u Yoɑbu tireru yoruɑ u Uri wɛ̃ u kɑ dɑ.
Win bwɑ̃ɑbun ɡuro ɡurobu bɑ nùn suuru kɑnɑ u kɑ se tem sɔɔn di, ɑdɑmɑ u yinɑ. Mɛyɑ u mɑɑ yinɑ u ɡɑ̃ɑnu di.
Adɑmɑ Amɔɔ kun Tɑmɑɑn ɡɑri yi wure. Mɑ u nùn tilɑsi kuɑ u kɑ nùn kpunɑ.
Sɑɑ ye Dɑfidin nukurɑ yɛmiɑ, win mɔru ye u kɑ Abusɑlɔmu mɔ̀ yɑ sure.
Mɑ Abusɑlɔmu u dɑ win yɛnuɔ, u ǹ de sinɑ bokon mi.
Mɑ sinɑ boko u Itɑi, Gɑtiɡii sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, mbɑn sɔ̃nɑ ɑ kɑ sun swĩi. A ɡɔsiro ɑ sinɑ Abusɑlɔmu u nun deemɑ. Domi wunɛ sɔɔwɑ. Yen biru bɑ kɑ nun nɑwɑ sɑɑ wunɛn tem di.
Mɑ Dɑfidi u nɛɛ, yɑ ǹ bɛɛ wɑ, bɛɛ Seruyɑn bibu. Durɔ wi, ù n mɑn wɔmmɔ yèn sɔ̃ Yinni Gusunɔ u nɛɛ u ko mɛ, wɑrɑ koo nùn yinɑri.
N deemɑ sɑɑ ye sɔɔ, Yonɑtɑm kɑ Akimɑsi bɑ wɑ̃ɑ Eni Roɡɛliɔ domi bɑ ǹ kɑ̃kɔ bu du wuuɔ ɡoo u bu wɑ. Yen sɔ̃nɑ bɑ rɑ wɔndiɑ ɡoo ɡɔri ben mi, u bu sɔ̃ kpuro ye yɑ koorɑmɔ, kpɑ be mɑɑ bu dɑ bu Dɑfidi sinɑ boko sɔ̃.
Yerɑ u dɛki itɑ suɑ yi yi nɔɔ sɛ̃u sɑ̃ɑ u dɑ mi dɑ̃ɑ te, tɑ Abusɑlɔmu sɔre. Mɑ u nùn yi sɔkurɑ win sɔndun deedeerɔ sɑnɑm mɛ u ǹ ɡinɑ ɡɔɔ kpɑ.
Mɑ ɡɑri yi, yi sinɑ boko wururɑ. Yerɑ u seewɑ u yɔɔwɑ ɡbɑ̃rɑrun ɡidɑmbisɑ wɔllɔ. Miyɑ u wɑ̃ɑ u sirenɛ u sumɔ u mɔ̀, nɛn bii Abusɑlɔmu, nɛn bii. Nɑ̀ n dɑɑ ɡu wunɛn ɑyerɔ, yɑ sɑnɔ bo. Nɛn bii Abusɑlɔmu, nɛn bii.
Sinɑ boko u nɛɛ, mbɑn sɔ̃nɑ nɑ mɑɑ ɡɑri dɛ̃ɛyɑsiɑmɔ, domi nɑ ɡɔ̃ru doke kɔ mɑ wunɛ kɑ Sibɑ i ko wunɛn debun tem mɛ bɔnu kowɑ.
Yen biru Yoɑbu kɑ win wɔnɔ Abisɑi bɑ wure bɑ Sebɑ nɑɑ ɡirɑ.
Beniwɑ Dɑfidi u Gɑbɑoniɡii be nɔmu bɛriɑ. Mɑ bɑ dɑ bɑ bu bwɛ̃ ɡuuru wɔllɔ Yinni Gusunɔn wuswɑɑɔ. Mɑ be kpuro bɑ ɡu sɔ̃ɔ tee te. Sɑɑ ye, yɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ dĩɑ ɡbiikinun ɡɛ̃ɛbun sɑɑ.
u kɑ mɑn doonɔ nɡe nim tori bɑkɑ.
U mɑn wɔrɑ yibɛrɛbɑn nɔmɑn di.
Ye Yinni Gusunɔ u mɔ̀, yɑ rɑ n dɛndewɑ.
Bɑ̀ n somiru kɑnɑ,
sunɔ wi u tɔmbu kpɑrɑmɔ ɡem swɑɑ sɔɔ,
Bɑ nùn bɛɛrɛ wɛ̃ too. Adɑmɑ u ǹ tɑbu durɔ ɡbiikobu itɑ be turɑ.
11-12 Sɑɑ yerɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u win sɔmɔ Gɑdi sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, ɑ doo ɑ Dɑfidi sɔ̃ ɑ nɛɛ, ɑmɛniwɑ nɛ Yinni Gusunɔ nɑ ɡerumɔ. Wee, nɑ nùn nɔni swɑ̃ɑru itɑ ɡɑɑ yiiye. Yen sɔ̃, u de u ɡɔsimɑ ten te u kĩ kpɑ n sere de tu koorɑ.
Ye Bɑti Sebɑ u turɑ mi, u yiirɑ sinɑ bokon wuswɑɑɔ. Mɑ sinɑ boko u nùn bikiɑ u nɛɛ, mbɑ ɑ kĩ.
Sɑlomɔɔ u mɑɑ sɔ̃ sinɑ ɡɔnɑɔ kɔ.
Mɑ Sɑlomɔɔ u nɛɛ, ɑ ɡeruo nɑ ǹ nun yinɑrimɔ.
Yenibɑn biruwɑ Sɑlomɔɔn bɑndɑ dɑm kuɑ.
Ye Isirelibɑ kpuro bɑ nuɑ nɡe mɛ sinɑ boko u siri bɑ nùn nɑsiɑ. Domi bɑ wɑ mɑ Gusunɔwɑ u nùn bwisi yi kɑ̃ u kɑ siri bi kuɑ.
Berɑ wɔkurɑ yiru yen wiruɡii berɑ, bɑ rɑ n kɑ dĩɑnu nɑɑmɔ ni Sɑlomɔɔ kɑ win tɔmbu bɑ rɑ di. Wɔ̃ɔ tiɑ sɔɔ, suru tiɑ berɑ bɑɑyere yɑ mɔ yu kɑ dĩɑnu nɑ. Bɑ ku rɑ de dĩɑnu nu biɑrɑ Sɑlomɔɔn yɛnuɔ.
Gidɑmbisɑ yen dii temkirun yɑsum mu sɑ̃ɑwɑ ɡɔm soonu nɔɔbu. Te tɑ mɑɑ wɑ̃ɑ suunu sɔɔ, teɡim mɑɑ ɡɔm soonu nɔɔbɑ tiɑ. Itɑseruɡim mɑɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ ɡɔm soonu nɔɔbɑ yiru. N deemɑ sɑ̃ɑ yee ten ɡɑnɑ yɑ sinum mɔ temɔ, ɑdɑmɑ ɡidɑmbisɑn dii temkirun wɔllɔ bɑ yen sinum kɑwɑwɑ ɡɔm soo teeru dɑɑsin dɑ̃ɑ yii yerun sɔ̃. Dii suunukirun wɔllɔ bɑ mɑɑ yen sinum kɑwɑ ɡɔm soo teeru dɑɑsin dɑ̃ɑ yii yerun sɔ̃. Bɑ yeni kuɑwɑ domi bɑ ǹ kĩ bu sɑ̃ɑ yee ten ɡɑnɑ yɑbɑ.
Sɑlomɔɔ u dii te bɑnɑwɑ wɔ̃ɔ nɔɔbɑ yiru.
Bɑ yen nɑɑ si kuɑwɑ nɡe tɑbu kɛkɛɡisu. Sin ɑkisi bɔrɑ kɑ yen mɔyo, kɑ yen uruu kɑ ɛrɛyɔ̃bɑ, bɑ ye kpuro kuɑwɑ kɑ sii ɡɑndu te bɑ yɑniɑ.
Yerɑ Isirelibɑ kpuro bɑ mɛnnɑ Sɑlomɔɔn mi, wɔ̃ɔn suru nɔɔbɑ yiruse wì sɔɔ bɑ rɑ tɔ̃ɔ bɑkɑru ɡɑru ko.
Nɛ kɑ wunɛn tɔmbu sɑ̀ n mɛnnɑmɑ yɑm mini, sɑ kɑnɑru mɔ̀, ɑ sun swɑɑ dɑkio, sɑɑ wɔllu di mi ɑ wɑ̃ɑ kpɑ ɑ sun suuru kuɑ.
Sɑlomɔɔ u kɛtɛ nɔrɔbun subɑ yɛndɑ yiru (22.000) kɑ yɑ̃ɑnu nɔrɔbun subɑ wunɑɑ teeru (120.000) ɡo u kɑ siɑrɑbun yɑ̃kunu kuɑ. Mɛyɑ bɑ kɑ Yinni Gusunɔ sɑ̃ɑ yee te wukiɑ.
Sɑɑ yè sɔɔ Sebɑn sunɔ tɔn kurɔ u nuɑ mɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u derɑ Sɑlomɔɔ u yĩsiru yɑrɑ, yerɑ u dɑ u kɑ Sɑlomɔɔn bwisi yin sɑkɑ mɛɛri kpɑ u nùn ɡɑ̃ɑ sɛ̃sɔɡii dɑbinu bikiɑ.
Sɑlomɔɔ u dɑ u Sidoniɡibun bũu wi bɑ mɔ̀ Asitɑɑte kɑ Amɔnibɑn bũu wi bɑ mɔ̀ Milikɔmu sɑ̃ɑmɔ.
Kpɑ u bwese kɛri tiɑ win bii wɛ̃ Dɑfidin sɔ̃ kpɑ u n dɑ n kɔsire mɔ bɑndu sɔɔ Yerusɑlɛmuɔ wuu ɡe u ɡɔsɑ bu kɑ nùn sɑ̃ mi.
Sɑɑ ye sɔɔrɑ u Adorɑmu ɡɔrɑ Isirelibɑn mi, wi u rɑ bu kpɑre bu kɑ yoo sɔmɑ ko. Mɑ bɑ nùn kpenu kɑsukɑ bɑ ɡo. Yerɑ n derɑ Roboɑmun tii, u win tɑbu kɛkɛ wɔri fuuku fuuku u dɑ Yerusɑlɛmuɔ.
Yerɑ u nɛɛ, bu win kɛtɛku ɡɑɑri bɔkuo.
Ye kurɔ wi, u tunumɑ, yerɑ Akiyɑ u win nɑɑsun dɑmu nuɑ win dii kɔnnɔwɔ. Mɑ u nɛɛ, ɑ duumɑ Yeroboɑmun kurɔ. Mbɑn sɔ̃nɑ ɑ tii ɡɔsiɑmɔ nɡe ɡoo. Wee Gusunɔ u mɑn yiire n nun lɑbɑɑri kɔ̃sɑ yeni sɔ̃.
Abiyɑmun tundo Roboɑmun wɑɑti sɔɔ, tɑbu kun kpɑ wi kɑ Yeroboɑmun bɑɑ sɔɔ.
Yen sɔ̃, Gusunɔ u koo win yɛnu kpeerɑsiɑ kpɑ ɡu ko nɡe Yeroboɑmu Nɛbɑtin biiɡuu.
Akɑbun wɑɑti ye sɔɔ, Hili Betɛliɡii u seewɑ u Yeriko bɑnɑ. Sɑɑ ye u wuu ɡen kpɛɛkpɛɛku swĩimɔ mɑ win bii ɡbiikoo Abirɑmu u ɡu. Sɑɑ ye u mɑɑ ɡen ɡbɑ̃rɑrun ɡɑmbo dokemɔ mɑ win bii dɑ̃ɑko Seɡubu u mɑɑ ɡu. N deemɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u rɑɑ ɡeruɑ Yosue Nunin biin nɔɔn di u nɛɛ, wi u mɑɑ wuu ɡe bɑnɑ, mɛsumɑ yɛ̃ron bibu bɑ koo ɡbi.
Mɑ Akɑbu kɑ Abudiɑsi, bɑ yɑm mi bɔnu kuɑ, bɑ yɑkɑ bekusu kɑso wɔri. Ben bɑɑwure u win swɑɑ mwɑ.
Mɑ bɑ kuɑ mɛ. Mɑ u mɑɑ nɛɛ, bu wureo bu nim mɛ wisi.
Mɑ dɔ̃ɔ u mɑɑ nɑ. Mɛyɑ Yinni Gusunɔ kun wɑ̃ɑ dɔ̃ɔ wi sɔɔ. Yen biru dɑmu piibu ɡɑɡɑ mɑɑ nɑ ɡe ɡɑ nɔɔbu do.
Isirelibɑn berɑ kɑ berɑn tɑbu kowo be, bɑ ɡbiɑ bɑ tɑbu yɑrɑ. Yerɑ Bɛni Hɑdɑdi u bikiɑ u nɛɛ, berɑ̀ mini. Mɑ bɑ nùn wisɑ bɑ nɛɛ, Sɑmɑrin diyɑ bɑ yɑrimɑ.
Sɑnɑm mɛ sinɑ boko u sɑrɔ win bɔkuɔ, yerɑ u nɔɔɡiru suɑ u nɛɛ, wee nɑ rɑɑ wɑ̃ɑ tɑbu sĩɑ sɔɔ, mɑ subɑru sɔɔ ɡoo u yɑrɑ u kɑ mɑn tɑbu durɔ ɡoo nɑɑwɑ n nùn kɔ̃su. U nɛɛ, nɑ̀ n derɑ durɔ wi, u doonɑ, nɛnɑ kon ko win kɔsire, ǹ kun mɛ, kon sii ɡeesun ɡobi nɔrɔbun subɑ itɑ (3.000) kɔsiɑ.
Domi ɡoo sɑri wi u tii yɔ̃su kɔ̃sɑ sɔɔ nɡe Akɑbu, Yinni Gusunɔn wuswɑɑɔ. N deemɑ win kurɔ Yesɑbɛliwɑ u rɑ n nùn dɑm kɛ̃mɔ u kɑ ye ko.
Yerɑ Misee u Akɑbu sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, ɑ Yinni Gusunɔn ɡɑri swɑɑ dɑkio, nɑ nùn wɑ u sɔ̃ win sinɑ kitɑru wɔllɔ. Mɑ win tɑbu kowobu bɑ yɔ̃ win nɔm ɡeu kɑ win nɔm dwɑrɔ.
Yosɑfɑti u ɡoo nimkusu dɑ̃kɑ si bɑ ko n dɑ kɑ wurɑ kɑso de Ofiriɔ. Adɑmɑ su ku rɑ turi mi, su rɑ kɔsirewɑ swɑɑɔ, wuu ɡe bɑ mɔ̀ Ɛsioni Gebɛɛɔ.
Mɑ Elisee u nùn wisɑ u nɛɛ, sere kɑ Yinni Gusunɔn wɑ̃ɑru kɑ mɑɑ wunɛn tiiɡiru nɑ ǹ nun derimɔ.
Yerɑ u bu sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, bu ɡbɛ̃ɛ kpɑɑru tɑmɑ bu bɔru doke te sɔɔ.
Yen sisiru bururu, sɑɑ ye bɑ kĩ bu bururun yɑ̃kuru ko, yerɑ bɑ wɑ wee, nim mu wee, sɑɑ Edɔmun berɑ ɡiɑn di, mu tem wukiri.
Yen biruwɑ kurɔ wi, u ɡurɑ suɑ u bii tɔn durɔ mɑrɑ wɔ̃ɔ kpɔɔ ɡe sɔɔ, ɡe Elisee u nùn burɑ.
Yenibɑn biru, durɔ ɡoo u nɑ sɑɑ Bɑɑli Sɑlisɑn di u kɑ Elisee pɛ̃ɛ nɑɑwɑ, ye bɑ kuɑ kɑ ɔɔsun som kpɑm kɑ sere mɑɑ dĩɑ bimi kpɛɛ ɡɛɛn sɑɑki tiɑ. Yerɑ Elisee u win sɔm kowo sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, u ye bɔnu koowo tɔn be bɑ wɑ̃ɑ min sɔ̃.
Nɑmɑni u nùn kɔkurɑ u nɛɛ, ɑ yɑnde kilo wɑtɑ suo.
Mɑ Siriɡii be, bɑ dɑ Eliseen mi. Yerɑ Elisee u kɑnɑru kuɑ u nɛɛ, Yinni Gusunɔ, ɑ bu wɔ̃koru kpɛ̃ɛyɔ.
Yerɑ sinɑ boko u seewɑ wɔ̃kuru u win bwɑ̃ɑbu sɔ̃ɔwɑ u nɛɛ, kon bɛɛ sɔ̃ bwisi yi Siriɡibu bɑ sun kuɑ. Bɑ yɛ̃ mɑ sɑ wɑ̃ɑ ɡɔ̃ɔru sɔɔ, yen sɔ̃nɑ bɑ ben sɑnsɑni deri bɑ dɑ bɑ kukuɑ yɑkɑsɔ, mɑ bɑ nɛɛ, bɛsɛ Isirelibɑ sɑ̀ n yɑrɑ bɛsɛn wuun di, kpɑ bu sun mwɛɛri wɑsiru. Yen biru bu du bɛsɛn wuuɔ.
Adɑmɑ Yinni Gusunɔ u ǹ kĩ u Yudɑbɑn bweseru kpeerɑsiɑ win bɔ̃ɔ Dɑfidin sɔ̃. Domi u rɑɑ nùn nɔɔ mwɛɛru kuɑ mɑ win bibun bweserɑ tɑ ko n wɑ̃ɑ bɑn te sɔɔ sere kɑ bɑɑdommɑɔ.
