1-2 Yehun bɑndun wɔ̃ɔ nɔɔbɑ yiruse sɔɔrɑ Yoɑsi u bɑndu di Yerusɑlɛmuɔ. U mɔwɑ wɔ̃ɔ nɔɔbɑ yiru sɑɑ ye sɔɔ. Mɑ u kuɑ wɔ̃ɔ weeru bɑn te sɔɔ. Win mɛron yĩsirɑ Sibiɑ Beri Sebɑɡii.
Ye Yoɑsi u kuɑn sukum kɑ wɔruɡɔɔ te u sɔ̃ɔsi, kɑ sere mɑɑ tɑɑ bi u kuɑ kɑ Amɑsiɑ Yudɑbɑn sinɑ boko, ye kpuron ɡɑri yi yoruɑ Isirelibɑn sinɑmbun fɑɑɡin tireru sɔɔ.
Mɑ u dɑ u wurɑ ɡurɑ, kɑ sii ɡeesu kɑ sere ɡɑ̃ɑ ɡee ni nu wɑ̃ɑ Yinni Gusunɔn sɑ̃ɑ yerɔ kɑ sinɑmbun ɑrumɑnin beru yerɔ. Yen biru u mɑɑ tɔmbu mɔɔru mwɛɛrɑ. Mɑ u ɡɔsirɑ Sɑmɑriɔ.
Yen biruwɑ Mɛnɑhɛmu wi, u wuu ɡe bɑ mɔ̀ Tifusɑki wɔri. Mɑ u tɔmbu ɡo sɑɑ Tirisɑn di n kɑ dɑ Tifusɑki mi. U Tifusɑki ye wɔriwɑ kɑ dɑm yèn sɔ̃ tɔn be, bɑ yinɑ u du ben wuuɔ, mɑ u ben ɡuriɡibun nuki bɛsukɑ.
Mɑ Akɑsi u sii ɡeesu suɑ kɑ wurɑ ye yɑ wɑ̃ɑ Yinni Gusunɔn sɑ̃ɑ yerɔ, kɑ sinɑmbun ɑrumɑni beru yerɔ. Mɑ u ye kpuro ɡurɑ u Asirin sinɑ boko wɛ̃.
Yudɑbɑn tii, bɑ ǹ Gusunɔ ben Yinni mɛm nɔɔwɛ. Isirelibɑn yirɑ bɑ swĩi mɑm mɑm.
Esekiɑsi Yudɑbɑn sinɑ boko win bɑndun wɔ̃ɔ nnɛse sɔɔ, kɑ mɑɑ Osee, Elɑn bii, Isirelibɑn sinɑ bokon bɑndun wɔ̃ɔ nɔɔbɑ yiruse sɔɔ, yerɑ Sɑɑmɑnɑsɑɑ Asirin sinɑ boko kɑ win tɔmbu bɑ Sɑmɑri tɑrusi wɔ̃ɔ yiru.
